    "_postman_id": "e65f04f9-7473-4d84-8d0c-bb6fc332f404",
    "name": "Booking App",
    "description": "# **📖 Booking App**\n\nThe **Booking App** is a backend system designed to manage hotel reservations with a secure, scalable, and user-friendly architecture. It provides endpoints for handling users, cities, hotels, images, bookings, and reviews, ensuring a complete ecosystem for a hotel booking platform.\n\n## **🎯 Purpose**\n\nThe goal of the Booking App is to simulate a real-world hotel reservation system, allowing users to:\n\n- Register and log in securely.\n    \n- Explore and filter hotels by city or name.\n    \n- Make and manage reservations.\n    \n- Share reviews and ratings.\n    \n- Access hotel images and details.\n    \n\n## **🏗️ Core Features**\n\n- **User Management:** Registration, login, profile updates, and secure authentication.\n    \n- **City Management:** CRUD operations for cities, with country codes for easy identification.\n    \n- **Hotel Management:** Search hotels by name or city, view details, and calculate average ratings from reviews.\n    \n- **Image Management:** Associate multiple images with hotels for richer content.\n    \n- **Booking System:** Create, update, and delete reservations linked to logged-in users.\n    \n- **Review System:** Post and manage reviews with pagination and filtering by hotel.\n    \n\n## **📊 Dataset**\n\nThe backend is seeded with realistic data to support testing and scalability:\n\n- 100 registered users\n    \n- 30 cities\n    \n- 150 hotels\n    \n- 300+ bookings\n    \n- 100+ reviews\n    \n- 300+ hotel images\n    \n\n## **🔒 Security & Access**\n\n- Public endpoints for browsing hotels, cities, and reviews.\n    \n- Private endpoints secured with authentication for managing users, bookings, hotels, and images.\n    \n- Smart queries and pagination for efficient data handling.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
